HEADWORD: Tapeline
<hw>Tape"line`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A painted tape,
marked with linear dimensions, as inches, feet, etc., and often inclosed
in a case, -- used for measuring.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

